Table contains following columns:

 - "Virtual machine"
 - "Test class"
 - "Result" - summarised general result of test with values "Succeeded" or "Failed"
 - "Passed" - sums of passed tests 
 - "Warnings" - sums of tests signed as warnings 
 - "Failed" - sums of failed tests
 - "File name"
 - "Export functions" - export all data of selected test into clipboard, JSON or PDF file

User can sort logs by Time date (default), Virtual machine, Test class, Results, number of Passed or Failed tests.
Details of each test is available by clicking on the table row, it expands (or hides) advanced information as Code of test, Name, Class, Result, Description, Actual and Expected values:
